      <div class="pop_close">[ 
        <a href="javascript:help_popup()">close</a> ]</div>
    </div>

    <div class="pop_content" style="display:none" id="pop_target_db">
      <p>Tomtom can search databases installed on the server or search a user 
      uploaded database in <a href="../doc/meme-format.html">MEME</a> DNA motif 
      format by selecting the "Upload Your Own Database" option. Uploaded 
      databases are searched in a queue and so require an email address. For 
      more information browse the <a 
      href="get_db_list.cgi?db_names=motif_db.csv&mode=doc&is_motif_db=1"
      >supported databases</a>.</p>
      <div class="pop_close">[ 
        <a href="javascript:help_popup()">close</a> ]</div>
